data.description: Terrific corner townhome with hardwoods in the living, tile in the kitchen, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and all-new stainless steel appliances. (Washer, dryer, fridge, dishwasher, and microwave included with the right offer.) Freshly painted and new carpet. Plenty of windows for indirect natural lighting. Recessed lighting in kitchen, crown molding. Fabulous master suite with sitting area and two walk-in closets. Split bedroom plan with vaulted ceilings. Low maintenance yard with patio and awning, HEB schools (5 mins into Bedford, Hurst, Fort Worth, Arlington, and Euless from the house) minutes to DFW Airport, Six Flags Over Texas, The Dallas Cowboys AT&T Stadium, and 25 Mins from Downtown Dallas or Fort Worth. Driving: 3 mins to Hwy 157, 5 mins to Hwy 121, 7 mins to Int 360, and 10 mins to Int 820. Radiant Barrier in Attic for low energy bills. Hurry, Relocation Seller. Buyer to verify schools, etc. (This Description was updated on 02/13/2023)
